text: "Down to the Honkytonk" is a 2018 song by country singer Jake Owen and is the second single from his sixth studio album Greetings from... Jake. It went to number 65 in the United States, number 58 in Canada and topped the country singles chart in Canada. ==References== Category:2018 songs Category:Country songs Category:Jake Owen songs
title: Down to the Honkytonk
